@startuml
title Product Creation Flow (Scented Candles)

actor User
participant "UI: Products Tab" as Products
participant "UI: Product Creator" as Creator
participant "API: Master Data" as API
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Products: Click "Create Product"
Products -> Creator: Open Product Creation Page
Creator -> API: Fetch Master Data (Fragrances, Containers)
API -> DB: Query Configurations
DB --> API: Return Configured Data
API --> Creator: Populate Dropdown Options

User -> Creator: Enter Basic Info (Name, Price, Cost, Weight)
User -> Creator: Select Container Type (from Master Data)

== Adding Fragrance Composition ==
User -> Creator: Select Fragrance (from Master Data)
Creator -> Creator: Add to Composition List
User -> Creator: Set Percentage for Fragrance
User -> Creator: (Repeat for additional fragrances)

== Validation & Saving ==
User -> Creator: Click "Save Product"
Creator -> Creator: Validate: Do all fragrance percentages sum to 100%?

alt Validation Failed
    Creator --> User: Show Error "Fragrance percentages must add up to 100%"
else Validation Passed
    Creator -> API: Submit New Product Data
    API -> DB: Insert Product Record
    DB --> API: Success
    API --> Creator: Success Notification
    Creator --> Products: Redirect to Products List
end

@enduml
